<section class="slide" data-name="p1" data-title="p1">
  <div class="content">
   <div class="container">
     <div class="wrap top">
      <ul class="flex left">
         <li class="col-12-12">
           <%= render "step5/sections/s3/title" %>
         </li>
       </ul>
       <ul class="grid left">
         <li class="col-5-12">
           <h3 class="big bold margin-bottom-2 ae-3 text-teal">Who does your syllabus serve?</h3>

           <h5 class="margin-top-5 uppercase semiBold margin-bottom-2 ae-1 text-yellow">
             <i class="far fa-stopwatch margin-right-1"></i>  5-minute exercise</h5>
           <ol class="list decimal margin-left-2 margin-top-2 margin-bottom-3 ae-3">
             <li class="margin-bottom-3">
               <h3 class="big light h3 ae-4">Write
                 <span class="text-teal bold">INSTITUTION</span>
                 next to sections required by your institution.
               </h3>
             </li>
             <li class="margin-bottom-3">
               <h3 class="big light h3 ae-4">
                 Write
                 <span class="text-teal bold">DEPARTMENT</span>
                 next to the sections required by your department.
               </h3>
             </li>
             <li class="margin-bottom-3">
               <h3 class="big light h3 ae-4">
                 Write <span class="text-teal bold">FACULTY</span> next to sections that explicate your
                  classroom rules/policies and the relationship you expect to have with students.
                </h3>
             </li>
           </ol>
           <div style="opacity: 0;">
             <p>As you deconstruct your syllabus, write down your observations — ideas, a-ha's, insights — and your sensemaking.</p>
             <p>Ask yourself: What is the process of deconstructing my syllabus helping me understand about who my syllabus serves?</p>
           </div>
         </li>
         <li class="col-5-12 ae-2"><img class="" src="<%= image_url("graphics/syllabus.svg") %>"/></li>

       </ul>
     </div>
   </div>
 </div>
</section>
